<br>
I would hire a few more GM's if I was them but I am not so I can't.<br>
<br>
People go on and on about Verant/SOE customer service like its intentional and designed to make peoples lives living hell. Yes, all corporations seek to make their customers as unhappy as possible.<br>
<br>
I /petition a few times a month, guides respond within 5 mins to 30 minutes, and they escalate promptly to a GM when needed. The GM is to the point, and helps me out.<br>
<br>
I am polite, they are helpful. Maybe I am missing something. It has been like this for 4 years now. <p><br>
